 494:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   * @brief  Disable I/O analog switch voltage booster.
 495:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   * @note   When voltage booster is enabled, I/O analog switches are supplied
 496:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         by a dedicated voltage booster, from VDD power domain. This is
 497:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         the recommended configuration with low VDDA voltage operation.
 498:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   * @note   The I/O analog switch voltage booster is relevant for peripherals
 499:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         using I/O in analog input: ADC, COMP, OPAMP.
 500:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         However, COMP and OPAMP inputs have a high impedance and
 501:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         voltage booster do not impact performance significantly.
 502:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         Therefore, the voltage booster is mainly intended for
 503:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   *         usage with ADC.
 504:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   * @rmtoll SYSCFG_CFGR1 BOOSTEN       LL_SYSCFG_DisableAnalogBooster
 505:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_system.h ****   * @retval None
